                <td style="width: 20px; height: 8px">
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Times New Roman;">
                <td style="width: 20px; height: 10px">
                </td>
                <td colspan="2" style="height: 10px;  text-align: justify">
                    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">
                        <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; font-size:10px;"><u>NOTE:-</u></b><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS"><span
                            style="font-size: 9pt">&nbsp;If this form is not sufficient to give relevant details, please attach another
                        paper duly signed by you.</span></span></p>
                </td>
                <td style="width: 20px; height: 10px">
                </td>
            </tr>
            
            
            <tr style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Times New Roman;">
                <td style="width: 20px; height: 10px">
                </td>
                <td colspan="2" style="height: 10px;  text-align: justify">
                    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in">
                        <span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Trebuchet MS">
                        1. <span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span>Please delete which is inapplicable</span></p>
                </td>
                <td style="width: 20px; height: 10px">
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Times New Roman">
                <td style="width: 20px; height: 10px">
                </td>
                <td colspan="2" style="height: 10px;  text-align: justify">
                    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in">
                        <span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Trebuchet MS; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman';
                            mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">
                            2. <span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span>Attach certificate of marriage if you are the spouse of the life assured</span></p>
                </td>
                <td style="width: 20px; height: 10px">
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="font-size: 12pt">
                <td style="width: 20px; height: 10px">
                </td>
                <td colspan="2" style="height: 10px;  text-align: justify">
                    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; text-align: justify;">
                        <span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Trebuchet MS; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman';
                            mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">
                            <span style="mso-spacerun: yes">3. </span>State 'deceased' at the relevant place if spouse/parents/brother/sister of the life assured has expired and attach the relevant death certificate.</span></p>
                </td>
                <td style="width: 20px; height: 10px">
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="font-size: 12pt">
                <td style="width: 20px; height: 10px">
                </td>
                <td colspan="2" style="height: 10px;  text-align: justify">
                    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in">
                        <span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Trebuchet MS; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman';
                            mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">
                            <span style="mso-spacerun: yes">4. </span>If the deceased life assured had children, please attach the certified copy of birth certificate of children</span></p>
                </td>
                <td style="width: 20px; height: 10px">
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="font-size: 12pt">
                <td style="width: 20px; height: 10px">
                </td>
                <td colspan="2" style="height: 10px;  text-align: justify">
                    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in">
                        <span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Trebuchet MS; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman';
                            mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">
                        <span style="mso-spacerun: yes">5. </span>If the deceased life assured had no children and the one or both the partners has have expired, please state the full names of brothers and sisters of the life assured and attach birth certificates</span></p>
                </td>
                <td style="width: 20px; height: 10px">
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="font-size: 12pt">
                <td style="width: 20px; height: 10px">
                </td>
                <td colspan="2" style="height: 10px;  text-align: justify">
                    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in">
                        <span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Trebuchet MS; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman';
                            mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">
                        <span style="mso-spacerun: yes">6. </span>Did the decease life assured keep a last will at the death. Does this insurance policy belong to the same. If the deceased had not kept a last will please inform us whether the deceased had a sufficient property for a testament and is there any testamentary case already processing with regard to the deceased’s property.</span></p>
                </td>
                <td style="width: 20px; height: 10px">
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="font-size: 12pt">
                <td style="width: 20px; height: 10px">
                </td>
                <td colspan="2" style="height: 10px;  text-align: justify">
                    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in">
                        <span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Trebuchet MS; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman';
                            mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">
                        <b>(All answers should be filled in legibly. Answers must be given in words. Strokes of pen or dots or dashes will not be accepted as answers. Any alterations or erasures must be certified with full signature)</b></span></p>
                </td>
                <td style="width: 20px; height: 10px">
                </td>
            </tr>
             
        </table>
        </div>
    </form>
</body>
</html>
